326
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:31,460
She has her own life

327
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:32,179
and future.

328
00:15:33,059 --> 00:15:33,620
Haitian.

329
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,059
