339
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,539
the world outside is vast?

340
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:53,860
Who told you to go out and see it,

341
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:54,700
to explore it

342
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:55,820
while you're still young?

343
00:16:00,340 --> 00:16:01,299
A tangible future you can grasp,

344
00:16:01,299 --> 00:16:02,700
or a maybe-love that might not be?

345
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:05,620
Which one do you choose?

346
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:09,580
You decide.

347
00:16:24,779 --> 00:16:27,220
Do you know that Macau

348
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:29,460
