00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:17,700
The day after tomorrow.

364
00:17:23,099 --> 00:17:24,579
I have a gift for you.

365
00:17:35,619 --> 00:17:37,579
Make every day meaningful.

366
00:17:38,299 --> 00:17:39,099
Meaningful.

367
00:17:42,980 --> 00:17:45,420
Thank you, Xueqing.

