411
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,140
the girl never imagined

412
00:20:28,220 --> 00:20:29,420
the boy would work so hard

413
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:31,500
to apply to the foreign university

414
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:33,619
she wanted to attend.

415
00:20:34,940 --> 00:20:37,740
And what the boy never expected

416
00:20:38,779 --> 00:20:39,980
was that the girl, for his sake,

417
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,579
