437
00:21:43,339 --> 00:21:45,619
May your journey ahead be filled with sunshine.

438
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:46,859
Go chase your dreams.

439
00:21:47,259 --> 00:21:48,740
I look forward to meeting you again.

440
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:09,059
Xueqing

